{"tid":1787762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度總理莫迪批評反對派修例事件上散佈謠言及煽動暴力","createTime":"2019-12-18T07:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T07:55:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a11178058daba8794c938278d6b12d5ee34ab227","tid":1787762,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"印度修訂《公民身份法》的爭議未平息。總理莫迪說修例後，對包括印度教徒、穆斯林、錫克教徒、基督徒及佛教徒在內的印度公民，沒有影響，又批評反對派在事件上散佈謠言及謊言，煽動爆力，不擇手段製造充滿「錯覺及謊言」的氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n當地最高法院押後處理指控修例違憲的案件，下月22日再開庭，聽取控辯雙方陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n根據經修訂的《公民身份法》，2015年前抵達印度，來自巴基斯坦、孟加拉、阿富汗三國，並信奉6種宗教的非法移民，獲得公民身份，只有穆斯林除外。國內批評政府意圖進一步「邊緣化」印度穆斯林，連日來全國各地都有民眾上街。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498321-20191218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498321-20191218.htm&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=21bc94ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498321-20191218.htm&h=2cb4ee16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498321-20191218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c43d4ad84a5b17496e1997018e4bd97edbfd0fb5","tid":1787762,"uid":19557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"印度手足 我地要connect 了"},{"pid":"5ac6188a6339e6ff9a5f52be7368f4d572753f54","tid":1787762,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"真係好似香港政府<br />\n<br />\n不停強姦婦女,殺人滅口<br />\n<br />\n再屈反對派修例事件上散佈謠言及煽動暴力"},{"pid":"c55928e058b0aa5b9696f508031d00157411479b","tid":1787762,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"耿爽（印度）"},{"pid":"dc5acfb70da33ef21a75486385af20e56b60f11e","tid":1787762,"uid":130797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"煽動爆力<br />\n<br />\n爆發力驚人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi